        E -->|JOIN on frame_id| F
        F["video_clips_gold\nframe_id · image_embeddings\nframe_description · frame_path\n(CDF enabled)"]
    end

    F -->|"Delta Sync\npipeline_type=TRIGGERED\nprimary_key=frame_id"| G

